DESCRIPTION:Weekly public gathering every Friday at Victory Cafe (Bloor+Bathurst) starting at 7:30 pm and going until approximately 10\, or until you make other plans. Look for the table with the horse figurine\, come sit down\, introduce yourself\, and meet people!\n\nStarts with people I've had a good conversation with in Toronto\, then anyone they've had a good conversation with\, too.\n\nBecause Toronto is full of interesting people who should bump into each other more often!
